<tool id="Vesicle model summary" name="Prints model summary" version="0.0.1">
  <description>of useful information and plots of parameters for a trained vesicular model.</description>
  <command interpreter="bash">
    vesicular_model_summary.sh $input
  </command>
  <inputs>
    <param name="model" type="data" label="Select a 3D vesicle model" help="Select a 3D vesicle model."/>
  </inputs>
  <outputs>
    <data format="zip" name="output" from_work_dir="output.zip"/>
  </outputs>
<help>

**Description**

Returns plots and description of a model.

-----

**Input**

- One 3D vesicular models generated by CellOrganizer

-----

**Output**

- Plots generated by model_summary in a zip of pdfs.
</help>
</tool>
